    "The money can then be transferred to these shell companies and it will be difficult to trace back to its original source. 3.",
    "Use offshore accounts: Offshore accounts are accounts located in countries outside the home country of the account holder.",
    "This provides an opportunity to hide money and make it appear as if it is from a legitimate source. 4.",
    "Use fictitious names: By using fictitious names, individuals can make transactions that are hard to trace.",
